WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.333
Blue bells melt across my tongue like electric snow.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.533
A triangle tastes of velvet thunder and silver dust.

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:18.183
I watch basslines bloom in violet glass behind my eyes.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:25.300
The red hum bends softly, perfuming the edges of time.

